org.gradoop.storage.common.api

Interface EPGMGraphPredictableOutput<GFilter extends ElementFilter,VFilter extends ElementFilter,EFilter extends ElementFilter>

  • Type Parameters:
    GFilter - graph element filter type
    VFilter - vertex element filter type
    EFilter - edge element filter type
    All Superinterfaces:
    EPGMGraphOutput

    public interface EPGMGraphPredictableOutput<GFilter extends ElementFilter,VFilter extends ElementFilter,EFilter extends ElementFilter>
extends EPGMGraphOutput
    Definition of predictable graph store output. A graph input instance provide a set of predictable query methods for EPGM Elements Only elements fulfill predicate will be return by table server side
    See Also:
    EPGM element query formula
